# Tara Horizon Theme — Complete Store Build Guide (US English)

This guide walks you through **every step** needed to build a new Shopify store with the Tara Horizon theme, from a blank store to a fully functional US English storefront.

> **Audience:** Developer or store operator setting up a fresh Shopify store.
> **Market:** United States (English).
> **Estimated time:** 4–6 hours for the full setup (excluding content creation).

---

## How This Guide Is Organized

Steps are ordered by **dependency** — each step builds on the previous one. Do not skip ahead.

| Phase | Steps | What It Covers |
|-------|-------|----------------|
| **A. Foundation** | 1–3 | Store account, theme upload, data architecture |
| **B. Content Structure** | 4–7 | Pages, blog, collections, products |
| **C. Configuration** | 8–11 | Templates, theme settings, navigation, apps |
| **D. Content & Launch** | 12–16 | Content entry, integrations, testing, launch |
| **E. Optional Add-Ons** | 17–18 | Store locator, pharmacy partners page |

