| `custom.whats_inside_content` | What's Inside Content | Rich text |
| `custom.free_of_heading` | Free Of Heading | Single-line text |
| `custom.free_of_content` | Free Of Content | Rich text |
| `custom.awards_heading` | Awards Heading | Single-line text |
| `custom.awards_content` | Awards Content | Rich text |
| `custom.fragrance_heading` | Fragrance Heading | Single-line text |
