| Namespace & Key | Display Name | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `custom.ingredients` | Ingredients | List of metaobject references → `ingredient` | Ingredient metaobjects linked to this product. Displayed in a carousel on the product page. |
| `custom.faqs` | FAQs | List of metaobject references → `faq_entry` | FAQ entries for this product. Rendered in an accordion. |

### 3.3 Article (Blog Post) Metafield Definitions

Navigate to **Settings > Custom data > Articles** and add these fields:

| Namespace & Key | Display Name | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `custom.featured` | Featured | Boolean | When `true`, eligible as the hero article on the blog listing page. |
| `custom.is_hero` | Is Hero | Boolean | Alternative hero flag used in blog grid filtering. |
| `custom.blog_summary` | Blog Summary | Single-line text | Custom excerpt for the hero card (overrides auto-excerpt). |
| `custom.read_time_override` | Read Time Override | Integer | Override auto-calculated reading time (minutes). Leave blank for auto (~230 words/min). |
| `custom.hero_caption` | Hero Caption | Single-line text | Caption below the featured image on the article page. |
| `custom.short_title` | Short Title | Single-line text | Short title for prev/next navigation (falls back to truncated title). |
| `custom.related_articles` | Related Articles | List of article references | Curated related articles. Falls back to recent posts if empty. |
| `custom.related_products` | Related Products | List of product references | Products for the "Shop the article" section. Hidden if empty. |
| `custom.author` | Author | Metaobject reference → `blog_author` | Rich author data. Falls back to `article.author` if not set. |
| `custom.ingredients` | Ingredients | List of metaobject references → `ingredient` | Ingredient metaobjects related to the article content. |
| `custom.listing_image` | Listing Image | File reference (image) | Custom listing image for blog cards. Overrides featured image in grid views. |
| `custom.hero_image` | Hero Image | File reference (image) | Override the featured image on the article detail page. |

