| *(Your Range 1)* | *(your-range-1)* | e.g., "Black Garlic + Ceramides" / `black-garlic-ceramides` |
| *(Your Range 2)* | *(your-range-2)* | e.g., "Onion + Peptides" / `onion-peptides` |
