## 7. Product Data Entry

For each product, populate the following fields:

### Minimum Required Fields

1. **Title** — Product name
2. **Description** — Full HTML product description (follow Tara Tone of Voice — see `.claude/skills/tara-tone-of-voice/SKILL.md`)
3. **Images** — Product photography (multiple angles recommended)
4. **Price** — Product pricing in USD
5. **`custom.tagline`** — Marketing tagline (appears across the entire site — homepage, collections, product page, quiz results)

### Recommended Fields

6. **`custom.short_description`** — Brief description for the product header
7. **`custom.size_ml`** — Volume display (e.g., "200ml" or "6.76 fl oz")
8. **`custom.ingredients`** — Link ingredient metaobjects (powers the ingredient carousel on the product page)
9. **`custom.faqs`** — Link FAQ metaobjects (powers the FAQ accordion)

### Product Accordion Content

Fill out the heading + content pairs for a complete product page experience. **If a heading is left blank, that accordion section is hidden** — use this to selectively show/hide sections per product.

| Fields | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `custom.key_benefits_heading` / `content` | Key benefits of the product |
| `custom.clinical_results_heading` / `content` | Clinical study results |
| `custom.how_to_use_heading` / `content` | Usage instructions |
| `custom.whats_inside_heading` / `content` | Ingredients overview |
| `custom.free_of_heading` / `content` | Free-of claims (sulfate-free, etc.) |
| `custom.awards_heading` / `content` | Awards and recognition |
| `custom.fragrance_heading` / `content` | Fragrance notes |

