## 13. External Integrations

### 13.1 Quiz AI Worker (Cloudflare Workers)

**Used on:** Quiz Results page (`/pages/quiz-results`)

The quiz system uses a Cloudflare Worker to process quiz answers and return AI-generated hair care recommendations.

