### 13.2 HubSpot Forms (Optional)

**Used on:** Pharmacy Partners page (see [Step 18](#18-pharmacy-partners-page-optional))

If you use the pharmacy partners page, configure:
- HubSpot Portal ID
- HubSpot Form ID
- Region: `na1` (North America)

