## 21. Launch

1. **Final review** — Walk through the entire site one more time
2. **Publish theme** — Go to **Online Store > Themes** and click **Publish** on the Tara Horizon theme
3. **Verify live site** — Check the live URL immediately after publishing
4. **Set up redirects** — If migrating from another site, set up URL redirects in **Online Store > Navigation > URL Redirects**
5. **Submit sitemap** — Shopify auto-generates a sitemap at `/sitemap.xml`. Submit it to Google Search Console.

